generate word
    pick a random word
    make a corresponding underscore string (array?)

update word
    update underscores on screen with word
    if called with a letter
        check letter in word with indexOf()
        if indexOf > -1



test letter
    (called every time button is pressed)
    test if letter is in word
    if in word:
        update word

